Package: neo4j.memory
Title: Neo4j Agent Memory Client for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Neo4j Labs", email = "labs@neo4j.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R client for neo4j-agent-memory, providing short-term, long-term,
    and reasoning memory operations via an HTTP transport layer. Built on R6
    classes with httr2 for HTTP and jsonlite for serialization.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/neo4j-labs/agent-memory-tck
